<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7492ed21-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7" identifier="/us/usc/t36/s140410"><num value="140410">§ 140410.</num><heading> Liability for acts of officers and agents</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The corporation is liable for any act of any officer or agent of the corporation acting within the scope of the authority of the corporation.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id7492ed22-3a70-11f1-9d9e-dfac6d46cab7">(Added <ref href="/us/pl/111/95/s1/a">Pub. L. 111–95, § 1(a)</ref>, <date date="2009-11-06">Nov. 6, 2009</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/123/3003">123 Stat. 3003</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
